'''贝达与巴尼亚斯屠杀'''（英语：Bayda and Baniyas massacres）是[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]中一场发生于[[2013年5月|2013年5月]]的屠杀，地点在叙利亚[[塔尔图斯省|塔尔图斯省]]的贝达（Bayda）和[[巴尼亚斯|巴尼亚斯]]（Baniyas）。根据报导，亲阿萨德的民兵组织对[[逊尼派|逊尼派]]的村庄及居住的城区进行屠杀。这场屠杀据推测是为了报复反对派稍早时候的一次攻击，那次攻击造成了数名士兵丧生。<ref name="heartland"/>在5月2日至3日，据报道有多个家庭在两起屠杀中遭到绝户，还有数千居民试图逃离。<ref>{{cite web |author=Peter Beaumont |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/may/04/syrian-sunni-families-die-in-assads-heartland |title=Syria: massacres of Sunni families reported in Assad's heartland |publisher=The Guardian |date=2013-05-04 |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2013-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130721173613/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/may/04/syrian-sunni-families-die-in-assads-heartland |dead-url=no }}</ref>估计至少100位平民被杀害，部分人士认为死亡人数可能超过400人。<ref>{{cite web |author=Stay informed today and every day |url=http://www.economist.com/news/middle-east-and-africa/21577394-things-go-bad-horrendous-big-outside-powers-call-talks |title=Syria’s civil war: The bloody stalemate persists |publisher=Economist.com |date=2013-05-11 |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019154438/https://www.economist.com/news/middle-east-and-africa/21577394-things-go-bad-horrendous-big-outside-powers-call-talks |dead-url=no }}</ref>人权观察组织认为在大规模处决当中有248人遇难。<ref>{{cite web |author=By AFP |url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/603773/syrian-forces-executed-248-in-two-villages-in-may-hrw/ |title=Syrian forces executed 248 in two villages in May: HRW |publisher=Tribune.com.pk |date=2013-09-13 |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125163807/https://tribune.com.pk/story/603773/syrian-forces-executed-248-in-two-villages-in-may-hrw |dead-url=no }}</ref>根据[[联合国|联合国]]的报告大约300到450人丧生。<ref>HRW [http://www.hrw.org/news/2013/09/13/syria-mass-executions-government-forces] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hrw.org/news/2013/09/13/syria-mass-executions-government-forces |date=20210506225732 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Nebehay |first=Stephanie |url=http://news.yahoo.com/syria-war-crimes-deepen-battle-territory-u-n-080613638.html |title=Syrian forces responsible for Banias massacres: U.N. report |publisher=News.yahoo.com |date=2013-09-11 |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2018-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106200408/https://news.yahoo.com/syria-war-crimes-deepen-battle-territory-u-n-080613638.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>幸存者证实是政府军在准军事武装[[國防軍_(敘利亞)|国家防卫军]]的支援下进入村庄并开始“凶残的攻击行动：纵火、劫掠和杀戮”。<ref name="bbc.co.uk">{{cite web |last=Pannell |first=Ian |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22684359 |title=Syrian activists document al-Bayda and Baniyas 'massacre' |publisher=BBC |date=2013-05-28 |accessdate=2013-10-21 |archive-date=2017-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171011152339/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22684359 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 政府军士兵遇袭 ==
早在2013年5月2日，在贝达村反对派武装与政府军展开交战。<ref name="sectarian">{{Cite web |url=http://www.myfoxaustin.com/story/22149543/syrian-opposition-blames-regime-for-village-deaths |title=Sectarian killings reported in Syrian village |access-date=2014-02-09 |archive-date=2013-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130507145921/http://www.myfoxaustin.com/story/22149543/syrian-opposition-blames-regime-for-village-deaths |dead-url=no }}</ref>活动人士声称一辆载有亲政府民兵（据悉是[[沙比哈|沙比哈]]民兵）的巴士遭到攻击，7人丧生，20至30人受伤。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://en.trend.az/regions/met/arabicr/2146620.html |title=Syrian troops storm "massacre" village |publisher=En.trend.az |date=2013-05-03 |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106041153/http://en.trend.az/regions/met/arabicr/2146620.html |archive-date=2014-01-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/afp/130502/dozens-killed-syrias-banias |title=Dozens killed in Syria's Banias |publisher=Globalpost.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304195630/http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/afp/130502/dozens-killed-syrias-banias |dead-url=no }}</ref>来自周边地区的叙利亚政府军和沙比哈民兵在下午赶到该地区并开始袭击这个村庄。

== 村庄遭袭 ==
政府军在亲政府武装分子的支援下攻入位于地中海沿岸山区中的贝达村，杀死了数十人，其中包括妇女和儿童，并焚毁了住宅。<ref>{{cite news|last=Lucas|first=Ryan|title=Dozens Killed By Assad Troops In Bayda Massacre, Syrian Activists Say|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/05/02/bayda-massacre-assad-syria_n_3203858.html|newspaper=Huffington Post|date=05/02/13|accessdate=2014-02-09|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305024531/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/05/02/bayda-massacre-assad-syria_n_3203858.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在军队攻入村庄前，政府军使用[[火箭弹|火箭弹]]轰炸了该村。<ref name="violence">{{cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2013/05/04/world/meast/syria-violence/index.html?hpt=hp_t1 |title=Sectarian violence reported in Syrian city of Baniyas |publisher=Edition.cnn.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2018-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180214202819/http://edition.cnn.com/2013/05/04/world/meast/syria-violence/index.html?hpt=hp_t1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

叙利亚人权观察组织声称至少50人，并且最多有可能达到100人，在这次暴力事件中丧生。目击者声称有些人是被刀或者钝器杀害的，还有数十名村民下落不明。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2318993/U-S-says-arming-Syrian-rebels-option-Assad-accused-killing-50-men-women-children-large-scale-massacre.html |title=Syrian dictator Assad 'massacres up to 100 men, women and children' with knives and guns as U.S says arming rebels is now an option |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2020-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316031405/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2318993/U-S-says-arming-Syrian-rebels-option-Assad-accused-killing-50-men-women-children-large-scale-massacre.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>之后，叙利亚人权观察组织声称他们有能力证明有51人被杀害。<ref>{{cite web |last=Fielding |first=Abigail |url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/a64a9bf0-b3f9-11e2-b5a5-00144feabdc0.html#axzz2SHCifszq |title=Opposition accuses Syria regime of massacre in coastal region |publisher=Ft.com |date=2013-05-03 |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2013-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130504130540/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/a64a9bf0-b3f9-11e2-b5a5-00144feabdc0.html#axzz2SHCifszq |dead-url=no }}</ref>另一份报告则能够证明72人被杀。<ref name="massacres">{{cite web |author=Jim Muir |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22410392 |title=Syrians flee 'massacres' in Baniyas and al-Bayda |publisher=Bbc.co.uk |date=2013-05-04 |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2017-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171205092814/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22410392 |dead-url=no }}</ref>反对派活动人士声称尽管贝达村是反对派控制的，但村里只有14名反对派武装分子。一名反对派活动人士说这次屠杀事件其实是对4天前附近地区另一起造成多名士兵丧生的袭击事件的报复行动。<ref name="heartland">{{cite web|last=Sherlock |first=Ruth |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/10036680/Syria-Sunni-village-massacred-in-Alawaite-heartland.html |title=Syria: Sunni village 'massacred' in Alawaite heartland |publisher=Telegraph.co.uk |date=2013-05-03 |accessdate=2014-01-06}}</ref>

受害者中包括贝达村前任伊玛目Sheikh Biyasi，他担任贝达村伊玛目长达30年。他被形容为“政府的忠实支持者，在两年前辞职之前由于他的政治观点而遭到人们的疏远。”根据一名幸存者的说法，“虽然他一直反对抗议活动，但他还是被杀害了”。Biyasi的家庭被[[路透社|路透社]]描述为遭受了“许多最严重的损失，能够证实有36名家庭成员遇害”。<ref>[[Reuters|Reuters]], 28 May 2013, [http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/05/28/us-syria-crisis-village-insight-idUSBRE94R08H20130528 Insight: Syrian village gives up secrets after dawn killings] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/05/28/us-syria-crisis-village-insight-idUSBRE94R08H20130528 |date=20151110030628 }}</ref>

== 巴尼亚斯屠杀 ==
5月3日，根据叙利亚人权观察组织说法，在巴尼亚斯市Ras al-Nabaa区发生了另一起屠杀事件，导致数百名逊尼派居民逃离了家园。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/world/348439/at-least-62-bodies-found-in-syria-banias-watchdog |title=At least 62 bodies found in Syria's Banias: watchdog |publisher=Bangkokpost.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/05/201354134851189993.html |title=Syrians flee coastal town after mass killings |publisher=Aljazeera.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2020-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729012144/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/05/201354134851189993.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>根据一份反对派的报告，总共有77名平民，其中包括14名儿童被害。<ref name="massacres"/>另两份报告则有名有姓的证实有96到145人被认定在该区被处决。<ref>{{cite web |author=The Violations Documenting Center in Syria |url=http://www.vdc-sy.info/index.php/en/martyrs |title=VDC Martyrs |publisher=Vdc-sy.info |date= |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006215053/http://www.vdc-sy.info/index.php/en/martyrs |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=369755133132831&set=a.150495128392167.28686.121855461256134&type=1 |title=145 civilians (34 children, 40 women, 71 men) killed in the Banias massacre |publisher=Facebook.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2016-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204123558/https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=369755133132831&set=a.150495128392167.28686.121855461256134&type=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在该区与反对派的交火中也有4名亲政府民兵和2名政府军丧生。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.facebook.com/syriaohr/posts/365811523527192 |title=Death toll for Friday 3/5/2013: More than 130 people killed yesterday in Syria |publisher=Facebook.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-06 }}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

国有媒体，声称政府军在该地区只是在搜寻和消灭恐怖分子。<ref name="violence"/>一名亲政府武装领导人Mihrac Ura声称有必要包围巴尼亚斯并将那些“叛徒”消灭干净。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/nownews/pro-regime-militant-speaks-of-cleansing-banias |script-title=en:Pro-regime militant speaks of “cleansing” Banias |publisher=Now.mmedia.me |date= |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2013-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203012954/https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/nownews/pro-regime-militant-speaks-of-cleansing-banias |dead-url=no }}</ref>政府军声称在贝达和巴尼亚斯总共消灭了40名恐怖分子。<ref>{{cite web |last=Pannell |first=Ian |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22684359 |title=Syrian activists document al-Bayda and Baniyas 'massacre' |publisher=Bbc.co.uk |date=2013-05-28 |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2017-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171011152339/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22684359 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

